{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344580/extras/\u5efa\u9020.gif?t=1735896999\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build a Village with Animal Companions</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your own village and recruit cute animal villagers to create a thriving community in the wasteland. Keep your villagers happy and satisfied by meeting their needs and watch them work hard for you in return.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344580/extras/\u63a2\u7d22.gif?t=1735896999\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore a Vast Game World</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture into a procedurally generated world alongside your animal companions. Gather diverse resources across different biomes and uncover the ruins of ancient civilizations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344580/extras/\u4e8b\u4ef6.gif?t=1735896999\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Face Unexpected Events and Challenges</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world is ever-changing! Be prepared to face various events and challenges with your companions: raider camps, mysterious dungeons, colossal mutated creatures, and other opportunity-filled yet perilous locations await your exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344580/extras/\u5347\u7d1a.gif?t=1735896999\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Upgrade Through Technological Research</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_parag